<p>
<note n="0989003" resp="#resp2" type="mod" target="#nkr_note_mod_0989003">探＝採【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note>
<note n="0989004" resp="#resp2" type="mod" target="#nkr_note_mod_0989004">貞＝真【明】，＝禎【宮】</note>
<note n="0989005" resp="#resp2" type="mod" target="#nkr_note_mod_0989005">慜＝愍【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note>
<note n="0989006" resp="#resp2" type="mod" target="#nkr_note_mod_0989006">開＝問【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note>
